<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>凡人修币录 S2 · EP1 渲染需求清单</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Serif+SC:wght@400;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+SC:wght@300;400;500&family=Share+Tech+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --gold: #D4A017;
    --gold-dim: #8B6914;
    --gold-bright: #F0C040;
    --dark: #080C14;
    --dark-2: #0D1220;
    --dark-3: #111827;
    --red: #E94560;
    --green: #2D6A4F;
    --green-bright: #2ECC71;
    --amber: #F0A500;
    --teal: #0E4D5C;
    --teal-bright: #1A8FAA;
    --text: #C8D0DC;
    --text-dim: #6B7280;
    --text-bright: #EEF2FF;
    --border: rgba(212,160,23,0.2);
    --border-bright: rgba(212,160,23,0.5);
    --priority-1: #E94560;
    --priority-2: #F0A500;
    --priority-3: #1A8FAA;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--dark);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Noto Sans SC', sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 48px 32px;
  }

  /* HEADER */
  .doc-header {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-bright);
    padding-bottom: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .doc-label {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--gold-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .doc-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-bright);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .doc-subtitle {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .doc-meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .doc-meta-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
  }

  .doc-meta-label { color: var(--gold-dim); }
  .doc-meta-value { color: var(--gold); }

  /* LEGEND */
  .legend {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: var(--dark-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .legend-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .legend-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* SECTION */
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--gold-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0 0 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    margin-top: 48px;
  }

  .section-title:first-of-type { margin-top: 0; }

  /* RENDER CARD */
  .render-card {
    background: var(--dark-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color 0.2s;
  }

  .render-card:hover { border-color: var(--border-bright); }

  .render-card-header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr auto;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .render-id {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gold);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .render-name {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-bright);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .render-scene {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .render-badges {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    align-items: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .badge {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .badge-p1 { background: rgba(233,69,96,0.15); color: var(--priority-1); border: 1px solid rgba(233,69,96,0.3); }
  .badge-p2 { background: rgba(240,165,0,0.15); color: var(--priority-2); border: 1px solid rgba(240,165,0,0.3); }
  .badge-p3 { background: rgba(26,143,170,0.15); color: var(--priority-3); border: 1px solid rgba(26,143,170,0.3); }
  .badge-done { background: rgba(46,204,113,0.15); color: var(--green-bright); border: 1px solid rgba(46,204,113,0.3); }
  .badge-char { background: rgba(212,160,23,0.1); color: var(--gold); border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .badge-scene { background: rgba(14,77,92,0.3); color: var(--teal-bright); border: 1px solid rgba(26,143,170,0.3); }
  .badge-fx { background: rgba(139,69,20,0.2); color: #E8835A; border: 1px solid rgba(232,131,90,0.3); }

  .render-body {
    padding: 0 20px 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  }

  .render-desc {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    padding: 16px 0 12px;
  }

  .render-details {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .render-detail-item {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
  }

  .render-detail-label {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--gold-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .render-detail-value {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .render-img-placeholder {
    background: var(--dark-3);
    border: 1px dashed var(--border);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 12px;
  }

  .render-img-placeholder-text {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }

  .render-img-done {
    border-radius: 6px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-top: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .render-img-done img {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
    max-height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  /* STATS */
  .stats-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .stat-card {
    background: var(--dark-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--gold);
    display: block;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  /* IMAGE LIGHTBOX */
  .lightbox {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.92);
    z-index: 1000;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    cursor: zoom-out;
  }

  .lightbox.open { display: flex; }
  .lightbox img { max-width: 90vw; max-height: 90vh; border-radius: 4px; }
  .lightbox-close { position: absolute; top: 24px; right: 24px; color: var(--text-dim); font-size: 20px; cursor: pointer; }

  /* PROGRESS BAR */
  .progress-bar {
    background: var(--dark-3);
    border-radius: 4px;
    height: 6px;
    margin-top: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .progress-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold-dim), var(--gold));
    border-radius: 4px;
    transition: width 0.3s;
  }

  /* NOTES */
  .note {
    background: rgba(212,160,23,0.05);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--gold-dim);
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-top: 12px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }


  /* TABS */
  .tab-nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-bright);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    margin-top: -20px;
  }

  .tab-btn {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    cursor: pointer;
    border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
    margin-bottom: -1px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .tab-btn:hover { color: var(--text); }

  .tab-btn.active {
    color: var(--gold);
    border-bottom-color: var(--gold);
  }

  .tab-page { display: none; }
  .tab-page.active { display: block; }

  /* SCREENPLAY */
  .script-wrap {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .script-scene {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--border);
    padding-left: 24px;
  }

  .script-scene-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .script-scene-num {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(212,160,23,0.1);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .script-scene-title {
    font-family: 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-bright);
  }

  .script-scene-meta {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-left: auto;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .script-location {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--gold-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .script-action {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .script-action em {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .script-dialogue {
    margin: 20px 0;
    padding: 0 32px;
  }

  .script-char {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .script-char.zhao { color: var(--gold); }
  .script-char.victor { color: var(--red); }
  .script-char.xiaozhu { color: #E879A0; }
  .script-char.robot { color: var(--text-dim); }
  .script-char.npc { color: var(--teal-bright); }
  .script-char.system { color: var(--teal-bright); }

  .script-paren {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .script-line {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text-bright);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .script-direction {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--teal-bright);
    background: rgba(26,143,170,0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(26,143,170,0.2);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    margin: 16px 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .script-divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin: 32px 0;
  }

  .script-end {
    text-align: center;
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gold);
    padding: 32px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-top: 48px;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
  }

  .script-flashback {
    background: rgba(212,160,23,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212,160,23,0.2);
    border-radius:6px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    margin: 16px 0;
  }

  .script-flashback-label {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    color: var(--gold-dim);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .script-countdown {
    font-family: 'Share Tech Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--red);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 24px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    animation: pulse 1s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.6; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    body { padding: 24px 16px; }
    .render-card-header { grid-template-columns: 60px 1fr; }
    .render-badges { display: none; }
    .render-details { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .stats-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="lightbox" id="lightbox" onclick="closeLightbox()">
  <div class="lightbox-close">✕</div>
  <img id="lightbox-img" src="" alt="">
</div>

<!-- HEADER -->
<div class="doc-header">
  <div class="doc-label">// 内部制作文件 · 请勿外传</div>
  <div class="doc-title">EP1 · 渲染需求清单</div>
  <div class="doc-subtitle">《凡人修币录》S2 · 第一集全场景渲染任务分配表</div>
  <div class="doc-meta">
    <div class="doc-meta-item">
      <span class="doc-meta-label">总渲染任务</span>
      <span class="doc-meta-value">37个</span>
    </div>
    <div class="doc-meta-item">
      <span class="doc-meta-label">已完成</span>
      <span class="doc-meta-value">2个</span>
    </div>
    <div class="doc-meta-item">
      <span class="doc-meta-label">版本</span>
      <span class="doc-meta-value">v1.0</span>
    </div>
    <div class="doc-meta-item">
      <span class="doc-meta-label">比例要求</span>
      <span class="doc-meta-value">全部 9:16 竖屏</span>
    </div>
    <div class="doc-meta-item">
      <span class="doc-meta-label">概念图相册</span>
      <span class="doc-meta-value"><a href="https://fanrenxiubi.imgbb.com/albums" target="_blank" style="color:var(--gold);text-decoration:none">fanrenxiubi.imgbb.com/albums ↗</a></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- TAB NAVIGATION -->
<div class="tab-nav">
  <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab('renders')">📋 渲染需求清单</button>
  <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('screenplay')">🎬 完整剧本</button>
</div>

<div class="tab-page active" id="tab-renders">
<!-- STATS -->
<div class="stats-grid">
  <div class="stat-card">
    <span class="stat-num">16</span>
    <div class="stat-label">A类·纯场景<br>无需定妆照</div>
    <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:12%"></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-card">
    <span class="stat-num">17</span>
    <div class="stat-label">B类·需要<br>角色定妆照</div>
    <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:0%"></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-card">
    <span class="stat-num">7</span>
    <div class="stat-label">C类·其他<br>角色镜头</div>
    <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:0%"></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="stat-card">
    <span class="stat-num">5</span>
    <div class="stat-label">D类·纯特效<br>后期制作</div>
    <div class="progress-bar"><div class="progress-fill" style="width:0%"></div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- LEGEND -->
<div class="legend">
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--priority-1)"></div><span>优先级1·第一批渲染</span></div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--priority-2)"></div><span>优先级2·第二批渲染</span></div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--priority-3)"></div><span>优先级3·第三批渲染</span></div>
  <div class="legend-item"><div class="legend-dot" style="background:var(--green-bright)"></div><span>已完成</span></div>
  <div class="legend-item"><span style="font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--teal-bright)">SCENE</span><span style="margin-left:4px">纯场景·无需定妆照</span></div>
  <div class="legend-item"><span style="font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--gold)">CHAR</span><span style="margin-left:4px">需要角色定妆照</span></div>
  <div class="legend-item"><span style="font-family:'Share Tech Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:#E8835A">FX</span><span style="margin-left:4px">后期特效</span></div>
</div>

<!-- A类 -->
<div class="section-title">A类 · 纯场景渲染（无需角色定妆照）</div>

<!-- A-01 -->
<div class="render-card">
  <div class="render-card-header">
    <div class="render-id">A-01</div>
    <div>
      <div class="render-name">永信城L2核心街区航拍</div>
      <div class="render-scene">场景A · 建立世界 · 第1镜头</div>
    </div>
    <div class="render-badges">
      <span class="badge badge-p2">优先级2</span>
      <span class="badge badge-scene">SCENE</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="render-body">
    <div class="render-desc">清晨，L2核心金融区。金色霓虹还未完全熄灭，K线图招牌在楼宇间闪烁。人流开始涌现。和任何一座现实城市没有区别——这是最重要的视觉原则。</div>
    <div class="render-details">
      <div class="render-detail-item">
        <div class="render-detail-label">视角</div>
        <div class="render-detail-value">航拍俯瞰，缓慢扫过</div>
      </div>
      <div class="render-detail-item">
        <div class="render-detail-label">色调</div>
        <div class="render-detail-value">金色霓虹为主，冷蓝天空，头顶隐约算法网格（极淡）</div>
      </div>
      <div class="render-detail-item">
        <div class="render-detail-label">关键元素</div>
        <div class="render-detail-value">K线山远景·K线图招牌·正常城市人流</div>
      </div>
      <div class="render-detail-item">
        <div class="render-detail-label">风格参考</div>
        <div class="render-detail-value">写实电影风·银翼杀手2049质感</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- A-02 -->
<div class="render-card">
  <div class="render-card-header">
    <div class="render-id">A-02</div>
    <div>
      <div class="render-name">天空中的巨型钟摆（平时状态）</div>
      <div class="render-scene">场景A · 建立世界 · 第2镜头</div>
    </div>
    <div class="render-badges">
      <span class="badge badge-p1">优先级1</span>
      <span class="badge badge-scene">SCENE</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="render-body">
    <div class="render-desc">永信城天空中悬挂的巨型钟摆。来回摆动，规律，缓慢。晨光从钟摆后透过来。街道上的人没有人抬头看它——它一直都在，像背景一样存在。这是它最恐怖的地方。</div>
    <div class="render-details">
      <div class="render-detail-item">
        <div class="render-detail-label">视角</div>
        <div class="render-detail-value">仰拍·钟摆占画面上方2/3</div>
      </div>
      <div class="render-detail-item">
        <div class="render-detail-label">色调</div>
        <div class="render-detail-value">清晨暖光·钟摆金属质感·冷蓝天空</div>
      </div>
      <div class="render-detail-item">
        <div class="render-detail-label">关键细节</div>
        <div class="render-detail-value">钟摆正在摆动（有运动模糊）·底部无红色针（平时不可见）</div>
      </div>
      <div class="render-detail-item">
        <div class="render-detail-label">重要说明</div>
        <div class="render-detail-value">钟摆是城市级别的尺度·人类在画面中极小</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- A-03 -->
<div class="render-card">
  <div class="render-card-header">
    <div class="render-id">A-03</div>
    <div>
      <div class="render-name">域峰广场外观全景</div>
      <div class="render-scene">场景A · 建立世界 · 第3镜头</div>
